1. *Grozan* ukus imao je taj sok. (This juice had a *terrible* taste.)
2. Tvoj odnos prema meni je *grozan*. (Your attitude towards me is *awful*.)
3. *Grozan* miris se širio iz kuhinje. (A *disgusting* smell was coming from the kitchen.)
4. Ne možemo izaći vani, vrijeme je *grozno*. (We can't go outside, the weather is *terrible*.)
5. Šta si uradio sa svojom kosom? Izgledaš *grozno*. (What did you do to your hair? You look *terrible*.)
6. Nisam uopšte spavao sinoć, osjećam se *grozno*. (I didn't sleep at all last night, I feel *awful*.)
7. Taj film je bio baš *grozan*. (That movie was really *terrible*.)
8. Ovo jelo je *grozno* za moje zdravlje. (This dish is *terrible* for my health.)
9. Tvoje ponašanje prema drugima je *grozno*. (Your behavior towards others is *awful*.)
10. Ne znam kako možeš slušati tu *groznu* muziku. (I don't know how you can listen to that *terrible* music.)